'''October 27''' is the 27th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . 

== Events ==
* {{ill|Hōki|ja|宝亀|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|771|ja|771|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Tōzan-dō|ja|Higashiyama Road|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} の{{ill|Musashi Province|ja|武蔵国|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} を{{ill|Tōkaidō|ja|東海道|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} に編入
== Births ==
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 2|ja|12月2日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Saitō Makoto|ja|斎藤実|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、30代{{ill|Prime Minister|ja|Prime Minister of Japan|1=Prime Minister of Japan|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ・{{ill|Admiral|ja|海軍大将|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} （+ {{ill|1936|ja|1936|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ）
== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Yoshida Shōin|ja|吉田松陰|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、{{ill|Philosopher|ja|Thinker|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} （* {{ill|1830|ja|1830|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ）

